With over 60,000 people in the New York shelter system, and over 20,000 of them being children, the work that @nyhomeless does with their annual Christmas Toy drive is not only so impressive , but also beyond inspiring and overwhelming (in the best way). Just like any other child, these children and their families deserve more than anything to receive great gifts and a smile on their faces every holiday season. To see how much time these incredible, hardworking, selfless women& men at the Coalition have put in year after year, inspires me to be of help wherever I can, and I hope it inspires you too!
